.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, volleyball, ice-hockey
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, doctor, videographer
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, japanese, mexican
 1. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3
 2. the japanese is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 4. the doctor is on the right of the japanese##1
 5. the japanese is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the doctor is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the japanese is on the left or right of the videographer##3
 9. the american is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
10. the dancer is on the left or right of the doctor##3
11. the dancer is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Sport         | volleyball    | rowing  | surfing | ice-hockey   |
| Job           | videographer | dancer   | doctor    | bartender |
| Nationality   | mexican      | japanese | brazilian | american  |

