.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple, watermelon, zucchini
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, lavender, amber
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, mystery, spy, western
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
8. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pineapple    | zucchini | broccoli    |
| Color         | lavender     | amber | aquamarine  | purple |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | western      | action   | spy         |

