.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, pilot, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, may, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, rowing, skateboarding
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | software-developer | lawyer        | engineer   | pilot  |
| Birthday   | august             | january     | december | may  |
| Sport         | lacrosse           | skateboarding | biathlon   | rowing |

