.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-15::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, raspberry
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, punk, trance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, february, december
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the person eating cucumber is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cherry is the fan of trance##1
6. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating cherry and the person who's birthday is in april##2
7. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cucumber | cherry    | raspberry | cranberry |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | trance    | punk      | blues     |
| Birthday     | march | february | december   | april      |

