1. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the prince-smoker##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the snowmobile##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
7. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | juice   | lemonade    | coffee      | almond-milk |
| Cigar       | swisher  | bongani | prince | siglo     |
| Transport   | scooter | ship        | snowmobile  | tram        |

