3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
6. the person eating mango is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growsaconite##1
8. the person eating asparagus is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | almond-milk | lemonade  |
| Food          | kale          | asparagus | mango       | kiwi      |
| Flower   | aconite     | begonia    | balloon-flower     | poppy |

