.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann, oliveros, tiparillo
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, skateboarding, surfing
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the blend-smoker and the oliveros-smoker##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Cigar    | oliveros | dannemann  | blend  | tiparillo           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Sport   | surfing   | golf       | biathlon | skateboarding  |

 